<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1901-09-14T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1901-09-14T00:00:00-05:00" n="478" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d478">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Sultan of Turkey</gloss> to
                                Mr. <persName type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Yildiz</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1901-09-14"><hi rend="italic">September 14,
                                    1901</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>I have learned with emotion of the tragic death of Mr. McKinley. I beg to
                            express to you the deep share I take in the sorrow caused by this
                            event.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Abdul Hamid.</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>